description:
This Christian Prison documentary depicts five formerly incarcerated men and their transformational journeys of faith. 

Rev. Mike Palombi, formerly incarcerated, leads an intriguing discussion with four men, on how they went from a life of addiction and crime to a life of humility and surrender, which positioned them to be used by God to bring transformation to the lives of men, struggling with similar circumstances and issues.

What God did for them, He can do for you, if you surrender your life to Him!
